text: Mittelhausen is a former commune. It is in Grand Est in the Bas-Rhin department in northeast France. On 1 January 2016, it was merged into the new commune of Wingersheim-les-Quatre-Bans.Arrêté 21 December 2015 == References == Category:Former communes in Bas-Rhin
title: Mittelhausen, Bas-Rhin
